    title: "Spiti's Ancient Fossils: Walking Through Prehistoric Seabeds",
    excerpt: "Discover how the high-altitude desert of Spiti Valley harbors remarkable marine fossils from when the Himalayan region lay beneath the Tethys Sea millions of years ago.",
    image: "/lovable-uploads/2687a820-b260-4b4b-b64a-eaa97ff88a5c.png",
    date: "January 12, 2024",
    author: "Vaibhav Reekhan",
    readTime: "3 min read",
