    title: "Spiti's Natural Hot Springs: Ancient Healing Waters",
    excerpt: "Experience the therapeutic mineral waters that emerge from deep within the Himalayas, offering natural respite from the cold and insights into traditional medicine practices.",
    image: "/lovable-uploads/96c75803-78e2-4f53-a67c-b14d8e80d30f.png",
